00:40:33,186 --> 00:40:37,315
Semua bilang kau pemimpinnya, Bongju.

494
00:40:38,733 --> 00:40:40,151
Namun, itu tak benar, ya?

495
00:40:47,450 --> 00:40:49,244
Tak bisa tidur di rumahmu sendiri?

496
00:40:49,327 --> 00:40:53,582
Benar. Orang tuaku pindah
ke Ilsan, jadi...

497
00:40:53,665 --> 00:40:55,876
Astaga, aku sungguh harus pindah.

498
00:40:56,209 --> 00:40:57,586
Pergilah cuci muka.

499
00:40:57,669 --> 00:40:59,462
Sudah tadi pagi.

500
00:41:00,422 --> 00:41:02,090
Itu kemarin pagi.

501
00:41:02,174 --> 00:41:04,843
Siapa peduli? Ini masih pagi.

502
00:41:05,927 --> 00:41:08,096
Astaga, aku lapar.

503
00:41:26,448 --> 00:41:27,532
Halo.

504
00:41:28,033 --> 00:41:29,492
<i>Kau menghubungi 2473?</i>

505
00:41:30,744 --> 00:41:32,495
Hai, Youngpil. Ini Yu Euijeong.

506
00:41:32,579 --> 00:41:33,830
Junmo...

507
00:41:33,914 --> 00:41:36,666
<i>Halo, Euijeong.</i>

508
00:41:36,750 --> 00:41:37,834
Apa kabar?

509
00:41:37,918 --> 00:41:39,294
<i>Baik, terima kasih.</i>

510
00:41:39,753 --> 00:41:42,506
Aku belum dengar kabar dari Junmo
sejak kemarin.

511
00:41:42,589 --> 00:41:43,965
Aku cemas.

512
00:41:45,383 --> 00:41:46,676
<i>Apa?</i>

513
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:47,928
Ada apa?

514
00:41:49,387 --> 00:41:52,474
<i>Dia cuti sakit karena asmanya.</i>

515
00:41:58,146 --> 00:41:58,980
Panas sekali.

516
00:41:59,105 --> 00:42:01,024
<i>Tekan satu untuk mendengarkan pesan suara.</i>

517
00:42:02,067 --> 00:42:03,693
<i>Ini aku. Apa kau sibuk?</i>

518
00:42:03,777 --> 00:42:06,655
<i>Aku tahu kau punya asma,
tetapi kita bisa makan, bukan?</i>

519
00:42:22,254 --> 00:42:23,254
Hei.

520
00:42:23,922 --> 00:42:27,092
Ada telepon mendesak dari teman.
Boleh aku makan siang sebentar?

521
00:42:32,305 --> 00:42:33,390
Hanya jika itu wanita.

522
00:42:34,307 --> 00:42:35,308
Memang wanita.

523
00:42:35,642 --> 00:42:37,561
Baik. Siapa dia?

524
00:42:39,104 --> 00:42:40,438
Mau kencan ganda?

525
00:42:42,899 --> 00:42:44,484
Pria tampan mendapat semuanya.

526
00:42:44,568 --> 00:42:45,902
Aku tak butuh mi...

527
00:42:46,862 --> 00:42:50,323
Benar. Makan dengan wanita
terasa lebih enak.

528
00:42:51,241 --> 00:42:53,994
Aku makan mi sendirian. Tak apa-apa.

529
00:43:01,209 --> 00:43:03,461
Euijeong, maaf aku tak beri tahu
sejak awal.

530
00:43:16,850 --> 00:43:18,226
Kini beri tahu aku.

531
00:43:19,394 --> 00:43:20,896
Apa kegiatanmu belakangan ini?

532
00:43:23,064 --> 00:43:25,442
Siapa yang membelikanmu jas
tanpa setahu istrimu?

533
00:43:25,525 --> 00:43:26,693
Bukan begitu.

534
00:43:31,364 --> 00:43:36,745
Jujur saja,
untuk menangkap penyelundup narkoba,

535
00:43:36,828 --> 00:43:38,830
aku menyamar dalam geng.

536
00:43:44,294 --> 00:43:46,755
Serius, itu kata mereka.

537
00:43:46,838 --> 00:43:48,715
Aku tak percaya...

538
00:43:52,802 --> 00:43:53,802
Halo, Pak.

539
00:43:54,888 --> 00:43:55,805
Hei, Seungho.

540
00:43:55,889 --> 00:43:57,432
- Ya, Pak?
- Kau sedang apa?

541
00:44:02,562 --> 00:44:04,814
Aku bertemu seseorang.

542
00:44:05,357 --> 00:44:08,485
Tunggu, aku mengenalnya dari SMA.

543
00:44:09,402 --> 00:44:10,904
Lucu melihat kalian di sini.

544
00:44:10,987 --> 00:44:12,280
Lama tak bertemu.

545
00:44:14,324 --> 00:44:15,325
Sudah lama.

546
00:44:16,701 --> 00:44:18,912
Dia temanku dari SD.

547
00:44:18,995 --> 00:44:20,747
Kami satu klub Taekwondo.

548
00:44:22,499 --> 00:44:23,708
Ini

549
00:44:24,334 --> 00:44:26,962
presiden perusahaan tempatku bergabung.

550
00:44:28,797 --> 00:44:30,048
Begitu?

551
00:44:30,465 --> 00:44:33,677
Gicheul setingkat di bawahku
di gereja saat SMA.

552
00:44:36,847 --> 00:44:38,098
Apa kabarmu?

553
00:44:38,765 --> 00:44:40,642
Baik, terima kasih.

554
00:44:41,893 --> 00:44:43,103
Apa rasanya menjadi polisi?

555
00:44:43,186 --> 00:44:44,813
Kau sudah tahu?

556
00:44:46,982 --> 00:44:48,525
Divisi apa?

557
00:44:49,568 --> 00:44:51,152
Divisi Keamanan Polisi Metro Seoul.

558
00:44:54,531 --> 00:44:56,116
Sudah selesai makan?

559
00:44:56,199 --> 00:44:57,200
Ya.

560
00:44:58,493 --> 00:45:00,120
Boleh aku membawa Seungho?

561
00:45:09,462 --> 00:45:12,799
Aku pergi dulu. Nanti kutelepon.

562
00:45:19,806 --> 00:45:22,225
Beraninya kau bertemu polisi, Berengsek?

563
00:45:22,309 --> 00:45:23,435
Bukan begitu.

564
00:45:23,518 --> 00:45:25,812
Kami dekat sejak SD.

565
00:45:26,354 --> 00:45:28,315
Ayahku pemadat,

566
00:45:28,398 --> 00:45:30,275
setiap dia teler dan memukuliku,

567
00:45:30,358 --> 00:45:33,069
aku biasa lari ke rumahnya.

568
00:45:33,153 --> 00:45:35,697
Kenapa menghubunginya, Bajingan?

569
00:45:36,198 --> 00:45:37,282
Sial!

570
00:45:37,365 --> 00:45:39,409
Aku tak menghubunginya.

571
00:45:40,702 --> 00:45:42,662
Dia menghubungiku lebih dulu.

572
00:45:44,372 --> 00:45:47,167
Kenapa polisi itu menghubungimu?

573
00:45:47,250 --> 00:45:49,127
Ayahku kena masalah karena pakai narkoba

574
00:45:51,213 --> 00:45:53,173
dan ditahan di Kantor Polisi Metro Seoul.

575
00:45:57,052 --> 00:45:58,220
Bos.

576
00:46:00,263 --> 00:46:02,015
Aku sungguh sulit percaya

577
00:46:02,098 --> 00:46:04,267
saat tahu kau dekat dengan Euijeong.

578
00:46:04,351 --> 00:46:06,436
Apa itu salahku?

579
00:46:10,398 --> 00:46:11,566
Ayo.

580
00:46:11,691 --> 00:46:13,151
- Seungho.
- Ya, Pak.

581
00:46:20,992 --> 00:46:23,328
Hormati Bos, Bajingan.

582
00:46:25,664 --> 00:46:26,831
Maaf.

583
00:46:42,931 --> 00:46:44,683
Ini aku, Euijeong.

584
00:46:44,808 --> 00:46:47,769
Kau terlibat penyelidikan sabu-sabu Junmo?

585
00:46:53,066 --> 00:46:55,819
Kau pikir aku akan percaya
ucapanmu, Seungho?

586
00:46:55,902 --> 00:46:56,902
Hei.

587
00:46:58,238 --> 00:47:00,574
Aku alergi polisi, tahu?

588
00:47:00,657 --> 00:47:02,284
Ayolah. Cukup.

589
00:47:10,333 --> 00:47:11,668
Harap maklum.

590
00:47:12,627 --> 00:47:14,546
Sepupu Taeho mendadak muncul,

591
00:47:14,880 --> 00:47:17,799
dan dia kebetulan tetangga

592
00:47:17,883 --> 00:47:19,968
teman gereja Bos saat SMA.

593
00:47:20,594 --> 00:47:22,596
Bahkan bagimu,
tidakkah itu terdengar aneh?

594
00:47:25,348 --> 00:47:28,768
Dunia kecil di Korea, ya?

595
00:47:31,438 --> 00:47:36,568
Gicheul, apa dia suka <i>tteokbokki</i>
dari kedai yang sama denganmu?

596
00:47:40,280 --> 00:47:41,698
Pasti begitu.

597
00:47:41,781 --> 00:47:44,701
Dia cinta pertama Bos
dan mereka lakukan semuanya bersama.

598
00:48:16,566 --> 00:48:18,443
Itu dari gerejaku saat SMA.

599
00:48:19,027 --> 00:48:20,612
Sebaiknya kubawa pulang.

